content:
I think there's been a misunderstanding! As a digital AI assistant, I don't have personal experiences, engage in physical activities, or participate in sports. I'm here to provide information and assist with your questions to the best of my abilities.

However, I'd be happy to help you create a sample workout plan that combines strength training, plyometric exercises, and cycling! Please let me know your specific goals, current fitness level, and any constraints you may have (e.g., available time, equipment, etc.). I'll do my best to provide a tailored plan that suits your needs.

Additionally, congratulations on your hat-trick and game-winning goal in your pick-up soccer game! That's an exciting achievement!
